'''Sallapadan''' is a 5th class [[Philippine municipality|municipality]] in the [[Philippine province|province]] of [[Abra province|Abra]], [[Philippines]]. According to the [[2000]] census, it has a population of 5,497 people in 1,075 households.

==Deng Barangay==

Ing Sallapadan atin yang 9 [[barangay]].

* Bazar
* Bilabila
* Gangal (Pob.)
* Maguyepyep
* Naguilian
* Saccaang
* Sallapadan
* Subusob
* Ud-udiao

